  <body>
    <p><ph conkeyref="reusables-transforming-documents/intro-for-transformation-tabs"/></p>
    <p>The <uicontrol>Options</uicontrol> tab allows you to specify the following options:<dl>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Working directory</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The path of the current directory of the Ant external process. <ph
              conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/specify-path-without-drop-down"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Build file</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>The Ant script file that is the input of the Ant external process. <ph
              conkeyref="reusables-user-guide/specify-path-without-drop-down"/></dd>
        </dlentry>
        <dlentry>
          <dt><uicontrol>Build target</uicontrol></dt>
          <dd>Optionally, you can specify a build target for the Ant script file. If no target is
            specified, the Ant target that is specified as the default in the Ant script file is
            used.</dd>
        </dlentry>
